Indentation is mentioned on page 69. It says that one should use 4 spaces as an indent and that the space key should be used instead of the tab key
because a mixture of the two can confuse python. Does Pycharm automatically convert tabs into 4 spaces?
    Pycharm automatically converts the tab key into 4 spaces
Why should there always be a newline after the last line of code?(PEP8)
    Just the convention, indicates that the file is finished, if the last blank line is missing, people might think that the file is damadged